          "comments": "Mozilla Firefox is not configured to disable Firefox accounts.",
          "finding_details": "#if [ -e /etc/firefox/policies/policies.json ];\nthen\n    echo \"/etc/firefox/policies/policies.json exists.\"\n    echo \"***XYLOK ICS***\"\n    cat /etc/firefox/policies/policies.json\nelse\n    echo \"/etc/firefox/policies/policies.json does not exist.\"\n    echo \"***XYLOK ICS***\"\n    if [ -e \"$ffinstloc/distribution/policies.json\" ];\n    then\n        echo \"$ffinstloc/distribution/policies.json exists.\"\n        echo \"***XYLOK ICS***\"\n        cat \"$ffinstloc/distribution/policies.json\"\n    else\n        echo \"$ffinstloc/distribution/policies.json does not exist.\"\n    fi\nfi\n\n\ud83d\udd0d /etc/firefox/policies/policies.json does not exist.\n\u274c /usr/lib64/firefox/distribution/policies.json does not exist.\n\n\nXylok post-processing completed with no errors.\n\n\nXylok post-processing completed with no errors.\n"
        },
        {
          "uuid": "f2ed9294-2213-484c-b502-3b77b201151c",
          "stig_uuid": "db7deaa8-52d9-4848-86ba-916c3bd75e68",
          "group_id": "V-251568",
