          "comments": "The 'telnet-server' package is not installed.",
          "finding_details": "#echo '***XYLOK ICS***'\nyum list installed telnet-server\n\nChecking if the 'telnet-server' package is installed:\n\u2705 The 'telnet-server' package is not installed.\n\n\nXylok post-processing completed with no errors.\n"
